# Who is *Incunabula* for?

*Incuanbula* is aimed at authors and publishers who wish to be have a light-weight, but rigorous editorial policy.

The workflow is designed to support multiple rounds of editorial interventions by many people, from shaping the structure of the book, to detailed criticisms of the content, right through to proof reading and final production.

The software itself is Open Source, and you can <a href="download and run it yourself.
